## Limitations

The report primarily focuses on the positive aspects of industrialization, which may present a skewed perspective. The negative impacts, such as environmental degradation and poor working conditions, are not covered in detail. Additionally, the sources used may vary in their depth of analysis and historical context, which could affect the comprehensiveness of the findings. Further research could provide a more balanced view by incorporating both positive and negative aspects of industrialization.